00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:07.440
What has he done to you? Why do you hate him so much?

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:08.880
Because he’s the Naga!

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:14.280
Let go of me.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:17.080
No, I’ll never leave you here.

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:20.040
What are you doing?! No. No! Phaya!

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:21.800
No. No!

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:23.520
Phaya!

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:27.280
Everyone that I love are taken away from me, all because of you.

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:28.920
It’s time for you to choose.

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:31.400
This is not just about Phaya, the man you love.

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:34.040
It’s about everyone that you love.

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:38.360
You know the whereabout of Montree and his every move...

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:40.640
because Chart is your spy?

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:41.360
That’s right.

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:43.800
I have recruited him to work secretly...

00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:45.600
after he didn’t pass the training at the camp.

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:50.000
Disguising himself as one of Montree’s people, I sent him to find more evidence on the drug network.

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:55.280
and also evidence on Tharn’s father’s murder as well as my brother’s and Lieut Tam’s cases.

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:57.120
That day we secretly went to investigate on the spider tattoo,

00:00:58.040 --> 00:01:00.720
Chart was also there. Was it your order?

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:03.120
If we had arrested Khom that day, everything would just end there.

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:06.280
We’d never able to get to Montree.

00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:10.080
Why didn’t you tell us anything, especially Tharn?

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:12.400
- If Tharn had known about this...
- Because I don’t trust anyone.

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:17.120
I can’t trust anyone even you.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:22.360
Lieut Tam died because someone in our unit tipped that information off.

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:23.880
Inspector.

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.760
Singh has tracked down Chart’s last location.

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.039
But it’s not clear.

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:32.800
We only know it’s close to our target area.

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.840
What about Phaya and Tharn, can you track them down?

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.280
Yes, they’re on the west side.

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:41.800
Only 5 kilometres away from Chart’s location.

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.880
Let’s split up into 2 teams.

00:01:45.479 --> 00:01:48.759
Yai, go look for Phaya and Tharn with the forest rangers.

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.920
The rest of you come with me. We’ll go arrest Montree.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:52.680
Yes, sir.

00:01:53.440 --> 00:01:54.320
Can you show me the map?

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:56.680
- Come here.
- What is it?

00:01:57.160 --> 00:01:58.080
Just come.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:01.080
What is it?

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:03.800
Here.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:12.440
Keep it for me first. Once everything is done, I’ll come back and put it on your ring finger.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:14.120
Don’t be so full of yourself.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:17.079
I’ve never said I would let you do that.

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.680
This mission is really dangerous. Please be careful.

00:02:22.240 --> 00:02:23.160
Yeah, you too.

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:26.360
(Incoming call)

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.720
Hello, babe.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:31.320
I’m with Tharn’s grandma right now.

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:32.840
Have you found him?

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:35.840
Not yet. We’d get going now.

00:02:36.079 --> 00:02:38.480
Okay, please find them.

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:42.960
Yeah. By the way, can you make me a spicy fish paste when I go back?

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:44.360
I want to eat it.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.079
Of course, I’ll make it for you.

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:51.560
Please come back soon. And promise me you’ll come back safely too.

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.360
Or else, I’ll throw it away. Got it?

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.160
Okay.

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:58.160
Please be careful.

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:14.160
He still hasn’t found them.

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:34.079
Please, let both of them come back safely.

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:43.040
I pray to all the holy spirits, please protect everyone and make them come back safely.

00:03:45.079 --> 00:03:52.040
Please protect Phaya and Tharn too.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:04:03.240
Dad, Mum. Please help protect Phaya and bring him back saftely.

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:07.840
I promise I will be good to him.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:12.080
And will listen to everything he says.

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:40.840
Got it.

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:42.760
Gather up, everyone!

00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:46.200
Let’s go, Yai.

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:47.080
Yes, sir.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:49.720
Yai, please find Phaya and Tharn.

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.280
Yeah, you guys be careful too.

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:55.080
I promise I’ll catch up to help arrest Montree.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:57.720
Let’s go.

00:04:58.159 --> 00:04:59.760
The rest of you, come with me.

