00:20:53.680 --> 00:20:56.960
If you have any evidence, just show it to me. Where is it?

00:20:58.360 --> 00:20:59.280
I don’t want to frame you.

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:00.640
I want you to confess.

00:21:01.440 --> 00:21:03.040
And you won’t be going to jail alone.

00:21:03.040 --> 00:21:05.040
I’m going to get that person behind you too.

00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:07.960
So, you better tell me how that person is.

00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:10.800
(Laughing)

00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:17.640
That person behind me?

00:21:17.840 --> 00:21:19.280
Why would you want to know?

00:21:19.280 --> 00:21:22.120
There is no one behind me!

00:21:22.120 --> 00:21:25.320
Let me tell you this, Inspector.

00:21:25.520 --> 00:21:29.240
It’s actually one of your kind who often comes wagging their tails...

00:21:29.240 --> 00:21:30.960
and begging me to help them.

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:36.440
I’m telling you justice, honesty justification they don’t really exist in this world.

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:38.480
Even though you could arrest someone like me,

00:21:38.480 --> 00:21:41.720
there’ll always be someone worse than me being born somewhere in this world.

00:21:41.720 --> 00:21:42.920
Do you know why?

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:45.520
Because there are some people who are worse than people like me.

00:21:45.520 --> 00:21:47.400
Some people like you lot...

00:21:47.560 --> 00:21:51.640
who always help facilitate those with money and power like me, Inspector.

00:21:51.640 --> 00:21:53.880
So, if you have any evidence, just lay it in front of me.

00:21:53.880 --> 00:21:55.200
I’m not afraid of you.

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:56.680
Fine.

00:21:57.520 --> 00:22:00.640
Then you can look forward to go rotting in jail.

00:22:02.120 --> 00:22:03.680
And let me tell you something.

00:22:03.840 --> 00:22:06.160
Justice, honesty, and justification

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:08.440
they do exist.

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:10.440
It’s up to the people who use them.

00:22:10.800 --> 00:22:11.560
Um

00:22:11.880 --> 00:22:13.120
Just wait and see.

00:22:13.120 --> 00:22:18.760
I’m going to crush these filthy network and put people like you behind bars.

00:22:19.560 --> 00:22:23.640
Then do it. Prove it.

00:22:27.200 --> 00:22:31.920
You might feel so sure that your power and money can help you to escape the hands of law this time.

00:22:33.800 --> 00:22:34.760
But trust me.

00:22:36.200 --> 00:22:37.960
You can never escape karma.

