Montree will be sentenced to prison for life.

00:23:56.080 --> 00:23:59.400
He is involved in many criminal cases including an international drug traffiking.

00:23:59.440 --> 00:24:02.160
A recent report also confirms that...

00:24:02.160 --> 00:24:06.120
several high-ranking police officers...

00:24:06.120 --> 00:24:10.000
as well as politicians are also involved in this case.

00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:16.200
IDF special investigation unit will reopen the murder cases of many ex-police officers...

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:21.280
in order to bring back justice for every one of them whose deaths are still shrouded in mystery.

00:24:21.840 --> 00:24:23.200
Phaya.

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:24.200
Tharn.

