Are you hurt anywhere?

00:24:33.640 --> 00:24:34.840
I’m safe and sound.

00:24:37.240 --> 00:24:39.360
- Miss you so much.
- Yai.

00:24:39.360 --> 00:24:41.440
Finally, you’ve made it.

00:24:42.760 --> 00:24:46.240
- I was so worried. Are you hurt?
- No.

